♪We hold onto the fire♪

263
00:17:20,180 --> 00:17:24,180
♪In our palms♪

264
00:17:25,500 --> 00:17:28,020
♪In the fog♪

265
00:17:28,740 --> 00:17:31,820
♪There's a nameless boat♪

266
00:17:32,220 --> 00:17:37,660
♪That understands where to go♪

267
00:17:38,380 --> 00:17:41,620
♪When the shadows are dispelled♪

268
00:17:41,940 --> 00:17:44,940
♪Fireflies will flicker♪

269
00:17:45,060 --> 00:17:51,820
♪Illuminating the twists and turns
along the journey♪

270
00:17:52,460 --> 00:17:59,020
♪Intertwined with you
in the wind and waves♪

271
00:17:59,540 --> 00:18:02,740
♪In the midst of ups and downs♪

272
00:18:02,820 --> 00:18:05,780
♪We drift together♪

273
00:18:06,220 --> 00:18:09,660
♪No matter how cold the glacier is♪

274
00:18:09,860 --> 00:18:12,980
♪No matter how deep the vortex is♪

275
00:18:13,220 --> 00:18:18,100
♪The dawn has never♪

